**Oval diamond pave band vs plain band:** The plain band solitaire puts 100% of visual weight on the center stone. The oval diamond pave band adds sparkle along the finger at a $150–$500 premium over a plain-band solitaire. For a 2ct oval, the center stone dominates either way. For a 1ct oval, the pave band adds meaningful visual presence to a stone that might otherwise look understated on the finger.

